# Red Team Tarot

Red Team Tarot is a cybersecurity-themed tarot engine that uses ATLAS attack mappings, OWASP LLM vulnerabilities, and randomized tarot-style card draws to generate dynamic attack narratives.

## MAKE SURE TO INSTALL THE requirements.txt

## Features

• 78-card deck covering Major and Minor Arcana  
• MITRE ATLAS mappings per card  
• OWASP LLM vulnerability mappings  
• Animated shuffle and card-flip sequences in terminal  
• Severity scoring with attack-type weighting  
• Text-based severity heatmap  

## How to Run

python3 run_tarot.py

